<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Metro Train Ticket Booking</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .train-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .train-info img {
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .train-info p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Metro Train Ticket Booking</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Metro Train Ticket Booking</h2>
        <p>Book your metro train tickets online with ease! Choose from our wide range of metro trains:</p>

        <div class="train-info">
            <img src="train1.jpg" alt="Train 1">
            <p>
                <strong>Train 1:</strong> Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                Suspendisse ut libero a urna mollis tristique. Donec facilisis odio sit amet felis
                laoreet, a euismod nisi sollicitudin.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="train-info">
            <img src="train2.jpg" alt="Train 2">
            <p>
                <strong>Train 2:</strong> Sed quis erat eu ligula efficitur vestibulum.
                Vivamus tempus mi id arcu volutpat, eu ullamcorper est mattis.
                Nam nec neque ut purus euismod fermentum.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="train-info">
            <img src="train3.jpg" alt="Train 3">
            <p>
                <strong>Train 3:</strong> Fusce consectetur ipsum nec est consequat venenatis.
                Nullam in odio vitae elit blandit interdum.
                Proin eu dui eu sem venenatis finibus sit amet non quam.
            </p>
        </div>

        <a href="#" class="btn">Book Now</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
